      "message": "why is this necessary? I\u0027m rusty on Go flags (last time touched them in early 2015), but looking at nearby existing code, just aliasing []string should be good enough: https://chromium.googlesource.com/infra/luci/luci-go/+/refs/changes/10/1375310/1/common/flag/int64slice.go#26 is it not?",
